{"word":"ἀλιτήριος","slug":"ἀλιτήριος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀλιτήριος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀλιταίνω'><el>ἀλιταίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>sinning</i> or <i>offending against</i>, a god, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>sinful, guilty</i>, <b><a href='S:Lysias'>Lys.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div>"}]}